{{> metabase/email/_header.hbs }}
<p>Hi {{userName}},</p>
<p>We deprecated Pulses in Metabase 0.38, two years ago.</p>
<p>Now the time has come to remove them.</p>
<p>On the next release, we will delete all Pulses and keep only Dashboard Subscriptions.</p>
<p>These are the active Pulses you have:</p>
<ul>
  {{#each pulses}}
    <li><a href="{{{this.url}}}">{{this.name}}</a></li>
  {{/each}}
</ul>
<p>You can replace legacy Pulses with <a href="https://www.metabase.com/docs/latest/questions/sharing/pulses">dashboards subscriptions and alerts</a>.</p>
<p>This message was sent to all Admins of <a href="{{instanceURL}}">{{instanceURL}}</a>.</p>
<p>Onward!</p>
<p>- The Metabase Team</p>
{{> metabase/email/_footer.hbs }}
